OL,6,GOfcom's decision to make no changes
OL,7,Gfor now to the rules covering the
OL,8,Gamount of advertising on ITV 1,
OL,9,GChannel 4 and Channel 5 is a huge
OL,10,Gsurprise.
OL,12,FThe regulator had been minded to
OL,13,Fallow the channels to show as much
OL,14,Fadvertising as other commercial
OL,15,Fbroadcasters.
OL,17,FIn other words, there could have been
OL,18,Fa full 12 minutes of ads in every
OL,19,Fdaytime and evening hour rather than
OL,20,Fmost of them.
OL,3,CPSB ad rules: Ofcom decides not to
OL,4,Cchange
