OL,6,FIt is highly unusual for Ofcom to
OL,7,Fchange its mind after revealing what
OL,8,Fit was minded to do.
OL,10,FSo what changed?
OL,12,FITV, STV and Channel 4 wanted the
OL,13,Ffreedom to show more ads. Channel 5's
OL,14,Fowner Paramount reiterated its
OL,15,Fopposition.
OL,17,FOne concern has been that the scheme
OL,18,Fcould lead to more small channels
OL,19,Fclosing.
OL,3,CPSB ad rules: Ofcom decides not to
OL,4,Cchange
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
