OL,6,FBut the views of sceptics and
OL,7,Fopponents had not changed in the past
OL,8,Ffew months.
OL,10,FNor was it somehow a revelation that
OL,11,Fchanges to the ad rules would
OL,12,Fprincipally mean changes to the
OL,13,Famount of advertising during the
OL,14,F"news hours". But how much would
OL,15,Fviewers have lost?
OL,3,CPSB ad rules: Ofcom decides not to
OL,4,Cchange
