OL,6,FBy my calculations, it is possible
OL,7,Fthe ITV Lunchtime News might have
OL,8,Flost 90 seconds. Ad breaks in the
OL,9,F10pm hour could have led to
OL,10,Fscheduling changes but would not
OL,11,Fnecessarily cut the overall duration
OL,12,Fof News at Ten.
OL,14,FThe biggest change would have been
OL,15,Fthe potential for an extra 6 minutes
OL,16,Fand 30 seconds of ads during a
OL,17,Ftypical evening in the 6pm hour.
OL,19,FBut it's only 19 months since ITV
OL,20,Fvoluntarily doubled the length of its
OL,21,Fearly evening news programme.
OL,3,CPSB ad rules: Ofcom decides not to
