OL,6,FITV would still have delivered on its
OL,7,Fstatutory obligations on news.
OL,9,FOn Monday, Channel 5 had 11 minutes
OL,10,F30 seconds worth of ads in the 5pm
OL,11,Fhour during which 5 News is shown.
OL,12,FWould a 30 second cut in the duration
OL,13,Freally have caused that much concern?
OL,15,FThe principal effect could have been
OL,16,Fon Channel 4 News as far as I can
OL,17,Fwork out.
OL,19,FEvery argument Ofcom highlights was
OL,20,Fknown about beforehand and
OL,21,Fscrutinised. There was never going to
OL,22,Fbe unanimity of opinion.
