OL,6,FThere is a legitimate argument to be
OL,7,Fmade for a holistic approach, looking
OL,8,Fat changes to ad rules along with
OL,9,Fbroader changes to the licensing of
OL,10,FITV and Channel 5. But, again, that
OL,11,Fcould have been said months ago.
OL,13,FBy taking things so far, there is the
OL,14,Frisk that Ofcom could be accused of
OL,15,Fleading stakeholders up the garden
OL,16,Fpath. It could have dismissed or
OL,17,Fdelayed the case for change much
OL,18,Fsooner.
