OL,6,FMeanwhile the value of commercial PSB
OL,7,Flicences continues to decline ` the
OL,8,Fgifted airspace and EPG prominence
OL,9,Fare less important than used to be
OL,10,Fthe case.
OL,12,FThe government has even raised the
OL,13,Fpossibility of allowing the three
OL,14,Fchannels to shift PSB obligations on
OL,15,Fto their digital channels and online
OL,16,Fservices.
