OL,6,FOf course, many of us may not like
OL,7,Fthe thought of more ads but there are
OL,8,Fcommercial realities to consider `
OL,9,Fpaying for PSB obligations and
OL,10,Fsustaining original British
OL,11,Fproductions. It's worth noting the
OL,12,Fchannels would not have been under
OL,13,Fany obligation to increase ad time.
OL,15,FIt is no bad thing to see Ofcom turn
OL,16,Fdown a commercial move favoured by
OL,17,Fsome broadcasters ` at least it shows
OL,18,Fthat the body is no lapdog.
OL,20,FBut I would not blame ITV or Channel
OL,21,F4 for being disappointed.
